{"tid":540112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(網絡孤島)「乘客與司機」女直播主與男友 涉網上散播色情內容被捕","createTime":"2018-01-25T07:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T08:31:13.000Z","uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd617f389602ea55e6dcd4e872133186e1de3112","tid":540112,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】內地直播為求出位，可說無所不用其極！內地一名直播主「東北二嫂」更因拍攝色情直播「乘客與司機打野戰」而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n內地警方近日破獲一個非法傳播色情內容的網路平台，拘捕一對男女。<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，該平台直播主與姓謝男友自編自導自演一段色誘「滴滴車」司機的片段，並在網上「爆紅」。</span><br />\n<br />\n湖南岳陽警方接報後開始監控，證實有關直播平台涉嫌散佈大量色情內容，該平台短短3個月就吸引了17.7萬名會員，「東北二嫂」就擁有1000多名會員，收入超過千萬人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n「東北二嫂」供稱，原本她也是做「正當直播」的，轉做色情直播後，初期收入也只屬一般。後來有觀眾建議她做「戶外」直播，於是她和男友就自編自導自演了「乘客與司機」。沒想到這段影片「爆紅」，「東北二嫂」突然變成網路熱搜，他們決定暫時收手，但已遭警方盯上，最終難逃法網。"},{"pid":"c766bbc9f483c218fb0ebb7571c6b52b94704ec2","tid":540112,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個互聯網+DEEP WEB傳哂先會黎到連登"},{"pid":"73271d88f3a946f4f71f18c09bbc92bb8b8b142e","tid":540112,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c766bbc9f483c218fb0ebb7571c6b52b94704ec2","tid":540112,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個互聯網+DEEP WEB傳哂先會黎到連登"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff05b84f008b9a9a647258c3f1712568d08a8bc6","tid":540112,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://5278.CC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F5278.CC&d=Q%2FfuHUrffkCmMTVCp%2FMfQ%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e115490d\" target=\"_blank\">5278.CC</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://52av.tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F52av.tv&d=Q%2FfuHUrffkCmMTVCp%2FMfQ%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dbf87d74\" target=\"_blank\">52av.tv</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個網既 自拍偷拍區大撚把大陸扑野直播，自己搵。"},{"pid":"34be80864b39de11120e9ba5ac8c85e982078deb","tid":540112,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545d0b40a50e9ff86d2faa7e059aef4e50f5795a","tid":540112,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73271d88f3a946f4f71f18c09bbc92bb8b8b142e","tid":540112,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c766bbc9f483c218fb0ebb7571c6b52b94704ec2","tid":540112,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個互聯網+DEEP WEB傳哂先會黎到連登"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"我地應該比金仔個內聯網快少少"}]}